nixosanywhere:
''NixOS Anywhere is used to install NixOS on any machine you have SSH access to.

- [Documentation](https://nix-community.github.io/nixos-anywhere/)
- [Repository](https://github.com/nix-community/nixos-anywhere)
- [Example Usage/Repository](https://github.com/nix-community/nixos-anywhere-examples)
- Matrix Room #nixos-anywhere:nixos.org''
random_xkcd: let rnd_xkcd_num = lib.mod (fromhex ("0x" + (builtins.substring 0 6 (builtins.hashString "md5" (builtins.toString builtins.currentTime))))) current_xkcd; in "https://xkcd.com/${builtins.toString rnd_xkcd_num}/"
votekick: x: if x == ''[@rasmus:rend.al](https://matrix.to/#/@rasmus:rend.al)'' then "Nej eyJhb" else "ja fuck 'em"
